2) REQUIREMENT
	2.1) Required Apache Module:
		 mod-rewrite
	2.2) Optional Apache Module:
		 mod-curl
	
3) INSTALL
	3.1) Create a new database 
	3.2) load the content of the file "db/redcms-default.sql"
	3.3) Edit config file index.php to provide db connection settings and the relative path to RedCMS

4) BUILD
	4.1) To build you need Apache Ant installed
	4.2) Then you will need to get YUI Builder <http://yuilibrary.com/projects/builder>  and copy it 
		at the root directory of your RedCMS install
	4.2) Then type "ant" in the command line at the root directory of your RedCMS install